response.original_title: NJPW Road To Power Struggle 2017: Day 8
response.overview: Day 8 of NJPW Road To Power Struggle 2017 was held on October 28, 2017, at Chichibunomiya Memorial Gymnasium in Fujisawa.  The main event featured Los Ingobernables de Japon (BUSHI, EVIL, Hiromu Takahashi, SANADA & Tetsuya Naito) vs CHAOS (Gedo, Kazuchika Okada, SHO, Tomohiro Ishii & YOH).  The card also featured Suzuki-gun (Minoru Suzuki, TAKA Michinoku & Takashi Iizuka) vs CHAOS (Hirooki Goto, Toru Yano & YOSHI-HASHI), and BULLET CLUB (Leo Tonga & Yujiro Takahashi) vs Ren Narita & Tetsuhiro Yagi.  Other wrestlers on the show include Dragon Lee, Ryusuke Taguchi, and Jushin Thunder Liger, and more!
